'''Bitcoin Unlimited''' (比特幣無限)是連接{{tsl|en|bitcoin network|比特幣網路}}的完整節點(full node)軟件客戶端。

與[[比特币核心|比特币核心]](Bitcoin Core)客戶端硬編碼的塊大小限制到1MB (1,048,576位元組)相比，
Bitcoin Unlimited刪除了區塊大小的限制，允許用戶通過協商來確定塊大小。它是比特幣協議硬分叉的一種，它可以從根本上解除區塊大小的限制。

Bitcoin Unlimited使用的協議是通過比特幣聯盟章程中描述的正式過程來管理。它是遵循已經發佈比特幣XT(Bitcoin XT)和比特幣經典(Bitcoin Classic)規範的一種替代協議，以便把比特幣的交易容量提高到大約每秒2.5-3次交易<ref name="acba">{{Cite news |url=http://www.coindesk.com/controversial-bitcoin-alternative-seeking-comeback/ |title=A Controversial Bitcoin Alternative is Seeking a Comeback |author=Alyssa Hertig |accessdate=17 January 2017 |date=25 September 2016 |work=CoinDesk |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118065947/http://www.coindesk.com/controversial-bitcoin-alternative-seeking-comeback/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Bajpai|first1=Prableen|title=What Is Bitcoin Unlimited?|url=http://www.investopedia.com/news/what-bitcoin-unlimited/|accessdate=8 November 2016|publisher=Investopedia, LLC|date=26 October 2016|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109021428/http://www.investopedia.com/news/what-bitcoin-unlimited/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

